<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-24">
      <img
        class="mx-auto h-auto w-full max-w-xl rounded-3xl"
        width="576"
        height="864"
        src="/PL/8028015-Photoroom.png"
        alt="Our mission to simplify academic formatting"
      />
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        <!-- Mission description -->
        <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Our mission</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              Our mission is to democratize academic writing and research publication. We believe that engineering students and research scholars should not have to face technical barriers or spend days fixing layouts just to format their documents correctly.
            </p>
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              By automating compliance for university templates like KTU and international publisher formats like IEEE, we enable researchers to focus on making scientific progress and writing great content rather than fighting margins or fixing LaTeX compiler errors.
            </p>
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              We are committed to building collaborative, easy-to-use, and highly reliable document editors that combine the simplicity of visual writing tools with the rendering power of publication-grade typesetting engines.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>


      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
